net.proteusframework.cms.component.content

Class ContentElementDataObjectCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.cms.component.content.ContentElementDataObjectCache

  • @Repository(value="contentElementDataObjectCache")
public class ContentElementDataObjectCache
extends Object
    Object cache for ContentElement data.

    This cache will not be *updated* when content changes since new entities are created in that case.

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
